sequenceDiagram
    title 時序圖 7/7 — 釋放控制
    %% 說明：Operator 離開駕駛艙 → Cockpit 釋放 ControlLease（狀態 RELEASED + releasedAt）
    %%       離開 LiveKit Room → Edge Agent 收到 ParticipantDisconnect Event →
    %%       停止 Go Publisher video → 進入 safe_mode（operator_disconnected）→
    %%       關閉 Session（狀態 CLOSED）
    %% 關鍵：Lease release → 中斷影片串流 → 關閉 Session，完整生命週期結束

    participant O as "操作員\nOperator"
    participant CP as "Web Cockpit\n(Next.js 3011)"
    participant API as "Backend API\n(Next.js 3010)"
    participant DB as "PostgreSQL\nDatabase"
    participant LK as "LiveKit SFU\n(v1.7.2)"
    participant EA as "Edge Agent\n(TypeScript)"
    participant GP as "Go Publisher\n(GStreamer + NVENC)"

    O->>CP: 離開駕駛艙
    CP->>API: POST /api/v1/vehicles/vehicle-001/control-lease/release
    API->>DB: 更新 Lease Status → RELEASED (releasedAt)
    DB-->>API: Done
    API-->>CP: Lease Released
    CP->>LK: 離開 LiveKit Room (disconnect)
    LK-->>EA: ParticipantDisconnect Event
    EA->>GP: IPC: stop (reason: user_left)
    GP->>LK: 停止 Video Track
    EA->>EA: enterSafeMode("operator_disconnected")
    EA->>API: POST /api/v1/sessions/close
    API->>DB: 更新 Session Status → CLOSED
